claim: Jessica Biel has acted in at least three comedy movies.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Biel has since starred in many films , including The Rules of Attraction  (  2002  )  , Blade : Trinity  (  2004  )  , Stealth  (  2005  )  , I Now Pronounce You Chuck & Larry  (  2007  )  , The A-Team  (  2010  )  and Total Recall  (  2012  )  .
